title: Mawaru Penguindrum - The One Who Will Bring Me Away (Doujinshi)
description:
A short Pixiv doujinshi of the couple KanbaxHimari from Mawaru Penguindrum. Terminally ill Himari Takakura wants to go outside with her brothers more than anything. However, that is a wish that won't come true. But Kanba refuses to accept that. Even if...

Original pixiv doujinshi: http://www.pixiv.net/member_illust.php?mode=medium&illust_id=23153796
